      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHADOW BAND (5) hit the ground running to score by 3.5 lengths (17.84) at this track over 305m. Harder here but looks a top chance again. COMPTON STELLA (8) goes very well at this journey here having never missed the frame including four wins and five placings. Hit the frame latest (23.30) when second at this track in a Grade 6. Makes strong appeal on best. JAJA DING DONG (2) turned in a plain run last time when fifth at this track over 305m behind Rocket Susie (18.42) in a Other. Was in the money the start prior. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Can figure in the finish. BLUE MOON MARIE (7) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
